parameters: "Oh, Ao and Hinori.. huh? Girls!? Seriously? That's so rockin'."
"Ahn Mr. Shirakita.. there, ah.. It's embarrassing.."

"Oh, this might not be good for education. Well, you guys are doing what
you're supposed to do, right?"
"..Please stop it already, in front of the child.."
"Sorry, this guy gets jealous so I'll see you later."
"I'll make sure to 'discipline' you properly, okay? Right, Satsuki?"
"..Hey, I'm curious about the two of your houses.. Can I go take a look?"
"Hey, come on.. give me a break."
".. Ah, you mean peeking..? That's.. a little.."

"Hehe~ You're doing such amazing things.. If you ever feel like it, just
let me know, okay?"
"Huh? Big brother.. and big sister? Hmm.. I see.."
